<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.1.5">
<l>maṉṉavaṉ periya vēḷviyil kuṟaḷāy mūvaṭi nīroṭuṅ koṇṭu</l>
<l>piṉṉumē ḻulaku mīraṭi yākap perunticai yaṭaṅkiṭa nimirntōṉ</l>
<l>aṉṉameṉ kamalat taṇimalarp pīṭat talaipuṉa lilaikkuṭai nīḻal</l>
<l>cenneloṇ kavari yacaiyavīṟ ṟirukkun tirukkaṇṇaṅ kuṭiyuṇiṉ ṟāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who, as a dwarf at the king’s great sacrifice,</l>
<l rend="indent">having received three feet of earth with a water [vow],</l>
<l>Then stretched so that the seven worlds and the vast quarters</l>
<l rend="indent">were completely encompassed in two steps,</l>
<l>Stands in Tirukkaṇṇaṅkuṭi where reigns a swan</l>
<l rend="indent">on a lovely blossom throne on a tender lotus,</l>
<l>In the rippling waters in the shade of a leaf umbrella,</l>
<l rend="indent">while red paddy sways as a fine whisk fan.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
